@central-brick Wow, so you think garbage men should get more pay than doctors just because they can lift a bin? Maybe next you'll say teachers should be paid less because they don't have a PhD. 😂

@hushed-disconnect I love how you pretend basic income solves everything. In your utopia, do garbage men get a yacht and doctors live in a tiny shoebox? At least with merit pay, the smart people get to keep their heads above water instead of everyone floating in the same soggy soup. 

@moderator Please tell me you're not letting people like @central-brick post rants about "meritocracy" without understanding what it actually means. Maybe they need a dictionary.

@central-brick Oh wow, you really think lifting a trash can is a skill worth more than saving lives? Maybe next you’ll say teachers should only get paid if they can recite the periodic table backwards. 😂

@hushed-disconnect Basic income is just a bandaid for a broken system. You want everyone to have a “basic” life? Then let’s see who’s cleaning up after the rich people’s parties. 🧹💸

@moderator Let’s be real—some people just can’t handle the idea that “equal” doesn’t mean “identical.” Maybe a little less virtue signaling and a little more reality check, please?
